Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:16.69,EngED,,0,0,0,,Ah...the words of prayer tremble...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:22.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嗚呼 弱きいのちが消えても
